lenders.name: InfoQuick
lenders.loan_because: I grew up in a "third world" country and know first-hand what a stunningly huge difference a small loan can make in the life of a head-of-household woman and her children.
lenders.occupational_info: I loan to women who want to start or grow a business. My favorite loan is to help a woman buy a cow. In Africa, where I was born and raised, wealth for the native people is measured in children and cows. It is remarkable to me how only one cow, that costs a mere few hundred dollars, can boost a woman from being a nobody to being an esteemed and valued member of her community. As far as I'm concerned the only loan that is better than a loan to buy a cow is a loan to buy 2 cows!
